Constructs a Tween

Parameters:
_tweenObject - the object you want to tween
_tweenObjectParameter - the parameter of the object you want to tween
_begin - the position you want the tween to begin at
_end - the position you want the tween to end at
_duration - how many seconds/frames you want the tween to take from begin to the end
_durationMode - SECONDS or FRAMES
_delay - how many seconds/frames you want the tween to delay before starting
